WEBVTT

00:01.823 --> 00:03.093
<i>The coroner said the remains</i>

00:03.094 --> 00:04.894
- should be here any minute.
- Daisy!

00:04.930 --> 00:08.031
Welcome back.

00:08.066 --> 00:10.934
Wow. You are so much bigger
than I expected.

00:10.969 --> 00:13.703
It looks like he might come out
dressed and ready for school.

00:13.738 --> 00:15.705
My doula assured me
that my meditation

00:15.740 --> 00:18.741
and my breathing exercises will
give me at least two more weeks.

00:18.777 --> 00:21.945
Well, you've been
through so much, losing Sweets.

00:21.980 --> 00:23.446
If you need to...
Thanks.

00:23.481 --> 00:25.281
I took the time I needed.

00:25.317 --> 00:27.550
Lance would want me
to rejoin the world.

00:27.585 --> 00:30.353
And the baby
and I have never felt better.

00:30.388 --> 00:32.021
You do seem very... Zen.

00:32.057 --> 00:34.524
I remember, at this point
I was driving Hodgins nuts,

00:34.559 --> 00:36.125
trying to get him

00:36.161 --> 00:37.593
to set up
Michael Vincent's room.

00:37.629 --> 00:39.529
Well, there's no rush.

00:39.564 --> 00:41.764
When he's ready, he'll tell me
how he wants his room set up.

00:41.800 --> 00:45.101
So, you're waiting until he can
talk before he has a room?

00:45.136 --> 00:47.770
Oh, my doula says
that a mother doesn't need words

00:47.806 --> 00:49.439
to communicate with her baby.

00:49.474 --> 00:52.208
Ah. This doula sounds

00:52.243 --> 00:55.545
like a... fascinating woman.

00:55.580 --> 00:57.180
Oh, she is.
She is.

00:57.215 --> 00:58.948
Ms. Wick?
Oh, over here.

00:58.984 --> 01:02.085
I'll get the remains
set up on the platform.

01:02.120 --> 01:03.453
This way.

01:03.488 --> 01:04.953
Okay.

01:04.989 --> 01:08.024
Who is that woman, and what
has she done with Daisy?

01:08.059 --> 01:10.326
Yeah.

01:13.531 --> 01:17.600
Apparently, the protesters
were at the fracking site,

01:17.635 --> 01:19.435
and they saw the remains
in the pit.

01:19.471 --> 01:22.372
Any idea how he or she ended up
in the fracking pit?

01:22.407 --> 01:25.375
No, but the protesters are
accusing the fracking company,

01:25.410 --> 01:27.677
which is mere supposition.
Well,

01:27.712 --> 01:29.812
the fracking people
are freaking, right?

01:29.848 --> 01:32.288
They have enough bad publicity
without dead bodies turning up.

01:32.317 --> 01:33.816
True.

01:33.852 --> 01:36.486
I recently read that in
Colorado, they have found a link

01:36.521 --> 01:38.121
between fracking
and increased seismic activity.

01:38.156 --> 01:39.722
All right, look.

01:39.758 --> 01:41.324
They're putting a lot
of pressure on the Bureau

01:41.359 --> 01:42.925
to get this solved quickly.

01:42.961 --> 01:44.961
Well, I'm sorry,
but I'm not gonna be as careless

01:44.996 --> 01:47.363
with my science
as they are about theirs.

01:47.399 --> 01:49.532
I believe that's everything.

01:49.567 --> 01:51.868
Yeah, everything that's ever
been made for a baby.

01:51.903 --> 01:54.270
Perhaps I've gone
a bit overboard,

01:54.305 --> 01:56.939
but this is...
Sweets' and Daisy's baby.

01:56.975 --> 01:59.275
I am totally with you
on this. You know what?

01:59.310 --> 02:01.044
We will be there for
every school play,

02:01.079 --> 02:03.146
graduation and hockey game.

02:03.181 --> 02:06.115
You're going
to be a good uncle, Booth.

02:06.151 --> 02:07.316
Thanks...

02:07.352 --> 02:08.818
Oh.

02:08.853 --> 02:10.119
Brennan. Yes?
Booth. Yeah.

02:10.155 --> 02:11.721
Okay.
On my way.

02:11.756 --> 02:13.523
Uh, 20 minutes.
Okay, I'll be... Great.

02:13.558 --> 02:16.259
All right, thanks. Bye.
All right, Stark. See you soon.

02:16.294 --> 02:18.661
Stark wants me in the office.
Cam needs me, too.

02:18.696 --> 02:20.096
Can you help me
get this to the car?

02:20.131 --> 02:21.564
Oh, whoa, not this!

02:21.599 --> 02:23.299
A classic. We got
to keep this!

02:23.334 --> 02:25.301
Oh, no.
Booth, are you serious?

02:25.336 --> 02:26.836
Come on, right?
Let's see if it works.

02:26.871 --> 02:28.538
What are we gonna
use it for?

02:28.573 --> 02:31.040
Bup, bup, bup, bup, bup, bup,
bup, bup, bup, bup, bup, bup.

02:31.076 --> 02:33.643
Bup, bup, bup, bup, bup,
bup, bup. Got to keep this.

02:35.847 --> 02:38.381
Given the narrow
subpubic concavity

02:38.416 --> 02:41.350
and the irregularly-lipped
ventral margin

02:41.386 --> 02:44.187
at the pubic symphysis, the
victim was male in his 40s.

02:44.222 --> 02:45.688
The left ulna was

02:45.723 --> 02:47.790
definitely fractured,
which explains the cast.

02:47.826 --> 02:49.358
But there's no
other damage evident

02:49.394 --> 02:51.494
that would give us
cause of death.

02:51.529 --> 02:54.263
I have a few little things for
the baby. I'll show you later.

02:54.299 --> 02:56.699
That's so nice. Thank you.

02:56.734 --> 03:00.103
I'm sure the baby can feel
your generosity.

03:00.138 --> 03:03.005
I doubt that very much.

03:03.041 --> 03:06.109
These bones are quite porous.

03:06.144 --> 03:07.743
I've uploaded the photos
of the remains

03:07.779 --> 03:09.145
from the coroner's report.

03:09.180 --> 03:10.613
These were taken

03:10.648 --> 03:13.716
on-site an hour ago.
- No.

03:13.751 --> 03:16.152
No, there must be some mistake.
These aren't the same remains.

03:16.187 --> 03:18.698
There's at least 20% more tissue
on the remains in the photos.

03:18.722 --> 03:19.523
No. These are

03:19.524 --> 03:21.891
definitely the photos from the
report, but I have never seen

03:21.926 --> 03:23.626
tissue loss
like this before.

03:23.661 --> 03:25.528
Hey. So, I just
performed a litmus test

03:25.563 --> 03:28.397
on the water that they brought
in from the fracking pit.

03:28.433 --> 03:30.366
The water in that pit
isn't just water.

03:30.401 --> 03:32.135
It's been spiked with
hydrochloric acid.

03:32.170 --> 03:34.737
Don't those sites use acid
as part of the process?

03:34.772 --> 03:36.172
But it's used in a much milder
concentration

03:36.207 --> 03:37.473
than what I just found.

03:37.509 --> 03:39.509
There must still be acid
on the remains.

03:39.544 --> 03:40.877
That's what's causing
the rapid tissue loss.

03:40.912 --> 03:42.512
No, no, no, don't...

03:42.547 --> 03:44.080
No one touch it until we know
what we're dealing with.

03:44.115 --> 03:46.949
But the acid is still consuming
the bones.

03:46.985 --> 03:48.618
You know, I'm on it.

03:48.653 --> 03:50.586
Maybe this is why the fracking
company was trying

03:50.622 --> 03:52.421
to get in the middle
of the investigation.

03:52.457 --> 03:54.417
Are you saying someone
from the company killed one

03:54.425 --> 03:56.585
of the protesters and is trying
to destroy the remains?

03:56.594 --> 03:57.994
There's no evidence of that.

03:58.029 --> 03:59.262
Soon we'll have no evidence
of anything.

03:59.297 --> 04:00.763
Okay.

04:00.798 --> 04:02.632
Stand back!
I got it. I got it. I got it.

04:05.303 --> 04:06.802
Wha...?

04:14.145 --> 04:15.711
Yeah.

04:17.015 --> 04:18.079
What have you done?!

04:18.116 --> 04:19.615
It's baking soda.

04:19.651 --> 04:22.218
It's not just
for cooking anymore.

04:22.253 --> 04:26.122
It should stop the acid from
eating the remains. I hope.

